* '''Player:''' Can I do it again?
* '''Atlas:''' What? Why?
* '''Player:''' It was fun, I'd like to do it again.
* '''Atlas:''' You're the first person to ask me that [player name]. I suppose I could train you again, but I will have to charge you the full 25,000 coins this time.
* {{topt|Yes}}
