* '''Player:''' Yes please.
* '''Atlas:''' You must take your training very seriously [player name]. This is the second time you'll have done this workout and paid full price!
* {{tact|Pay Atlas 25,000 coins to train again?}}
* {{topt|Yes}}
** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|No}}
** {{tact|end}}

===Subsequent training sessions===
